{
    "$comment": "agentpad13 Rev A (PCB v4_r27) - vial-qmk port. Pin map regenerated from the definitive per-GPIO table in hardware/pcb/v4/ORDER-READINESS.md (Layer 4, extracted twice from the final board copper: netlist + pcbnew). rgb_matrix.layout coordinates are generated by firmware/gen_led_layout.py from the v4_r27 LED centroids (chain: 0-12 per-key SW1-SW13, 13 layer indicator, 14-23 underglow).",
